    } \
    -cleanup {
      $FH_LAST ServiceDelete TEST
    } \
    -returnCodes    error \
    -match	    glob \
    -result         {[cC]> (client-0) \[transaction-callback-error] <Token|TEST>, <Num|1>
[sS]> (server-0) \[*pBufferGetA4] type ERROR, it is not allowed to convert an 'WID' object into an 'INT' object
